        <dd><span class="self-citation-authors">Dumontier M, Gray AJG, Marshall MS, Alexiev V, Ansell P, Bader GD, Baran J, Bolleman JT, Callahan A, Cruz-Toledo J, Gaudet P, Gombocz EA, Gonzalez Beltran AN, Groth P, Haendel M, Ito M, Jupp S, Juty N, Katayama T, Kobayashi N, Krishnaswami K, Laibe C, Le Novère N, Lin S, Malone J, Miller M, Mungall C, Rietveld L, Wimalaratne SM, Yamaguchi A.</span> <span class="self-citation-year">2017</span>. <span class="self-citation-title">The health care and life sciences community profile for dataset descriptions</span>. <span itemprop="isPartOf" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/PublicationVolume"><span class="self-citation-journal" itemprop="isPartOf" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Periodical"><span itemprop="name">PeerJ Preprints</span></span> <span class="self-citation-volume" itemprop="volumeNumber">5</span></span>:<span class="self-citation-elocation" itemprop="pageStart">e1982v2</span> <a href="https://doi.org/10.7287/peerj.preprints.1982v2" itemprop="url">https://doi.org/10.7287/peerj.preprints.1982v2</a></dd>
